Kuba Trump yaremeye burundu uko ibibazo byagenze, byashyizwe mu rujijo mu mipaka y'ishyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'abanyamakuru bashinja icyizere Amerika ifite cyo kwinjiza ibikoresho by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ingenzi, mu Bushinwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mico y'ingendo z'indege bwakoreshejwe mu gukora amakarita no guhanura ibipimo byo gukwirakwira, bwashyizwe ahagaragara mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Binyuze ku makuru yo mu 2018 ya International Air Transport Association, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo byari bifite umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byavuzwe ko ari ahantu hazwi cyane ku bantu bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragaye ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke mu bihugu 20 by'ingenzi mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Australia yagaragaye ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi.
Yavuze ko hakiri byinshi byo kumenya kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, mu gihugu cya Australia hatangajwe ko hari imimerere y'ubutabire bw'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko imodoka zitwara abantu zihagaritswe neza mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu bitandukanye byateganyaga gukura abaturage babyo n'abadipolomate mu karere, mbere na mbere binyuze mu ndege z'ubwishyu z'igihugu cy'iwabo, nyuma yo kurekurwa n'ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Arjantine, Ubudage na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere bigamije gukuraho abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazavanaho abaturage bose bavuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yakuye 34 muri bo cyangwa abagize umuryango wabo uretse Abanyapolonye bane, Umushinwa n'Umuhindi.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde baramanutse muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yahagaritse mbere yo gukomeza urugendo rwayo rwo kujya muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (176 bo mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bo mu ndege ya kabiri ya leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan maze boherezwa ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Trenton Air Force Base kugira ngo bagume mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 baturutse i Wuhan, yageze ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada i Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Australia bajyanye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare muri Kigo cya Gereza cya Christmas Island, cyaje kongera gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cyo gushyirwamo abantu mu kato, aho bagumye iminsi 14.
Indege yo kuvana abaturage ba New Zealand yageze i Auckland ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe bo muri Australia na Pacific) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'ingabo z'isi cya Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zari gukura Abanyamerika ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 bo muri Kanada bari bavuye muri Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye gukura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yatewe inkunga na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yashubije mu gihugu cyayo abaturage 112 ba Afurika y'Epfo.
Ivuriro ryakozwe mbere yo gutwara abantu, maze Abanyarwanda bane bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basiga inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyarwanda b'Abanyafurika y'Epfo bonyine bagaragaye ko badakora neza ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibisubizo by'ibigeragezo byakijije abantu bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abasirikare b'indege, abapilote, abakozi bo muri hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu gikorwa cy'ubutabazi, bagumye mu isanzure ry'ibitaro no mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Resort The Ranch.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Irak mu buryo bufatiweho bitewe n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byohereje ubufasha mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri Kaminuza z'Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza ubufasha ku bantu bagizweho ingaruka na virusi mu Bushinwa, hamwe n'itsinda rihuriye mu gace ka Greater Chicago bivugwa ko ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu Ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi bw'abantu Direct Relief, uhuza na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'uburinzi bwa bwite, harimo ingofero n'ikapu, binyuze mu gutwara indege byihutirwa ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje inkunga ya miriyoni 100 z'amadolari ku kigo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye cyita ku buzima (OMS) yo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo n'imihati yo kuzirinda, ndetse no kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge y'i Singapour yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa ka miliyoni imwe i Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko izatangaza miliyoni 18 z'amakanzu y'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10.000 yo kwirinda, Amerika yohereje toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi isezeranya izindi miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu bufasha bw'amafaranga ku bihugu byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo. Nyuma y'uko ubwandu bwabaye mu Bushinwa, igihugu cyakomeje kohereza ubufasha mu bihugu bitandukanye byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu gufasha u Butaliyani gucunga icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima abantu miliyoni 1.1 n'amasiki y'amaso miliyoni 6 n'imyenda y'uburinzi ibihumbi 60 i Addis Abeba muri Etiyopiya kugira ngo ishyirwe mu bikorwa na Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje ibikoresho 5000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'imashini 5 zo guhumeka mu gihugu cya Panama.
