Urugero, Espagne yavanye ibikoresho 58000 byo gupima Coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa ku gipimo cyo gutunganya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwasubije udupfukamunwa 600.000 twaguye mu cyuma.
Ububiligi bwafashe udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudashobora gukoreshwa, twavugwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'u Bushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha bwihutirwa ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimiye imbaraga z'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yabonye itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwa kutaha amakuru yatumye ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kugabanya ibizabagora, n'ikibazo cy'ubu, aho guverinoma y'u Bushinwa "yahaye abaturage ibisobanuro buri gihe kugira ngo birinde imvururu z'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya".
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu rwego rwo kwamagana icyemezo cy'abayobozi bakuru cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko "ibyo nta gushidikanya ko bitari inama ya OMS" kandi ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'icyifuzo cyo guhashya icyorezo mu gace cyari gikorerwamo cyane". Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko icyorezo cyanduye abantu benshi hanze y'u Bushinwa ndetse n'umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cyabaye nk'Icyorezo cy'Ubuzima bwa Leta ku Isi (PHEIC), cyabaye icya gatandatu cya PHEIC kuva icyo cyorezo cyatangira gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ibicurane mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko PHEIC yiswe kubera "akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ayigereranyije n'abari mu bihugu bifite gahunda z'ubuzima zidakomeye.
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo kugira ingamba zitangiza bidafite ishingiro ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "OMS itishimiye kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira imyiteguro y'ingamba mu bihugu bifite amikoro make no hagati, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gufasha ibyo bihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye iyi virusi, ndetse n'iyo yaba yaboneka".
Tedros yatanze ibisubizo nyuma yaho avuga ko "turi abanyembaraga nk'umugozi wacu udakomeye" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "guhora ushyiraho ubu cyangwa uzajya wishyura nyuma". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, AntÃ³nio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'umutungo wose w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye nk'igisubizo".
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku bibazo by'umutekano (UN Crisis Management Team) watangiye gukora, bituma habaho guhuza ibikorwa byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, OMS ivuga ko bizatuma "bashobora kwibanda ku bibazo by'ubuzima mu gihe ibindi bigo bishobora kwinjiza ubumenyi bwabyo mu mibereho y'abaturage, ubukungu n'ingaruka z'iterambere z'iki cyorezo".
Ku wa 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'umurimo wa WHO hamwe n'Ubushinwa ryemerewe guha ubufasha inzobere mpuzamahanga na WHO ku butaka mu Bushinwa mu gucunga mu rugo no gupima "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'iki cyorezo" binyuze mu mahugurwa n'inama n'inzego zikomeye ku rwego rw'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo gusura kugira ngo "basuzume ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'uturere, harimo imiterere y'imijyi n'icyaro". Ku wa 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi yagombye gukora byinshi kurushaho kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cya Coronavirus gishobora kuba", ivuga ko nubwo byari hakiri kare cyane gutangaza icyorezo, ibihugu byagombye no gushyiraho "ingamba yo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kiri gutera imbere muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'umurimo wo gupima imimerere. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abakozi ba OMS bavuze ko igenzura ry'igitero cya Coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi yose ryazamuka kuva "ryisumbuye" kugeza "ryisumbuye cyane", ni cyo gipimo cyo kwirinda no gupima ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi bw'imimerere y'ivutu, yavuze mu itangazo ati "Iki ni ikiganiro cy'ibanze kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba kuba mwiteguye", avuga ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yavuze ko ibipimo by'ubu nta ruhushya rw'abayobozi b'ubuzima bwa rusange bafite rwo gutangaza icyorezo cy'icyorezo ku isi hose, avuga ko ibyo byasobanuraga ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'iki cyorezo".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS "yahangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo bidasanzwe byo gukwirakwira no gukomera, ndetse n'ibipimo bidasanzwe byo kudakora". OMS yahuye n'ibyamaganwe byinshi kubera ibyo yabonye nk'ubuyobozi butari bwiza bw'icyorezo, harimo gutangaza mu gihe cy'igihe kitari gito ko ari ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Muri icyo gikorwa harimo no gusaba Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ko azamukuramo, ashyirwaho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'umuryango w'abibumbye ku burenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu zemeza ko uburenganzira bw'umuntu wese bubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Iri tsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira icyo akora kugira ngo akize ubuzima kandi ko leta ari yo izabibazwa.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura uburyo cyangwa gahunda y'ubuzima bitagomba na rimwe kuba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni ku itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abatari bake, abageze mu za bukuru, abafite ibibazo byo mu mutwe, abatagira aho baba, abafite ubukene bukabije, abafunzwe, ndetse n'impunzi n'abandi bantu batamenyekanye bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage z'ikibazo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe ubufatanye n'iterambere ry'ubukungu watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru y'igihe kandi yuzuye ku bibazo by'ingamba za politiki mu bihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Mu migambi yo gukomeza imibare y'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi yose mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibihe by'igifungo n'ibice byo ku rugendo, ikigo cya digitale kirimo ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ingamba, gifasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi kandi bigatuma habaho igisubizo gikoranabuhanga ku isi hose ku kibazo cya Coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro ku bijyanye no gucunga icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibiza cyatangiye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'akarere k'ishyaka rya communiste chinoise (PCC) bakatiwe kubera uburyo bakoreshaga mu bikorwa byo gushyira mu kato abantu bo mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko batishimiye uko leta yafashe icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu bitangazamakuru bavuga ko iki gikorwa cyabayeho kugira ngo umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa Xi Jinping arinde umujinya w'abaturage ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'u Bushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian banze ko Coronavirus yatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'igitekerezo cy'umugambi w'ivugurura kuri COVID-19 byaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwavuze ko Coronavirus ari "Virus yo mu Bushinwa" cyangwa "Virus yo mu mujyi wa Wuhan" buvuga ko kuba Ubushinwa bwaragabanyije virusi "yahindutse icyorezo cy'icyorezo ku isi hose", ibyo bikaba byaravumwe n'abashakashatsi bamwe na bamwe ko ari urwikekwe n' "uburyo bwo guhungabanya ubutabera mu kurwanya iki cyorezo".
