Byatangiriye inama ko twagombaga kugerageza no kubona ubwo butumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, harimo inama z'itangazamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibikoresho nk'ibi bya Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byerekana ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza ubufasha mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bigize ikiganiro cyo kugira ingaruka ku isi yose.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga y'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi, Josep Borrell, yavuze ko hari "ingingo ya politiki irimo n'intambara yo kugira uruhare binyuze ku myifatire y'ubwibone n'imiyoborere y'ubuntu".
Borrell yavuze kandi ko "Ubushinwa burimo busakaza ubutumwa ko butandukanye n'Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ushyira mu gaciro kandi wiringirwa".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika guhagarika ibihano byafatiwe Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko bwohereje ubufasha muri ibyo bihugu.
