Ibiganiro bya COVID-19 ni porogaramu za software zigendanwa zo gufasha mu gukurikirana mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abafitanye isano") bashobora kuba barahuye n'abantu banduye.
